title: S2 E3: Psy vs. Psy with Mel Damski
description:
This week, Maggie and Tim are joined by director Mel Damski to talk about Season 2 Episode 3: Psy vs. Psy. The episode where the FBI bring in a new psychic to compete with Shawn and Juliet gets her flirt on with Lou Diamond Phillips.
